ermarket whether it is Safeway, Lucky’s, Trader Joe’s, World Market, Walmart, Target, Food4Less, Sprouts and Raley’s. We also cover any local food chains like Lion’s Market, Mitsuwa, Meat 4 All, Taj Mahal etc.[/content_box]\r\n[content_box title="Delivery Rates"  image="" icon="money"]Deliveries rates are $9.95, $7.95 and $4.95. To be specific, $9.95 will be the starting range and customers who have order more than 10 times/month will qualify for $7.50 per delivery rate for a minimum order of $25 and no maximum.[/content_box]\r\n[/content_boxes]\r\n\r\n[/fullwidth]\r\n\r\n[fullwidth menu_anchor="" backgroundcolor="#E9EAEE" backgroundimage="" backgroundrepeat="no-repeat" backgroundposition="top left" backgroundattachment="fixed" bordersize="0px" bordercolor="#e5e4e4" paddingTop="20px" paddingBottom="20px"]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center; font-size: 31px !important;color: #666 !important;">HUGE SELECTION OF GROCERY ITEMS</h1>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 24px !important; color: #666 !important;">We carry a wide range of grocery items of over 3000 products.</p>\r\n[/fullwidth]\r\n\r\n[fullwidth menu_anchor="" backgroundcolor="#fff" backgroundimage="" backgroundrepeat="no-repeat" backgroundposition="top left" backgroundattachment="fixed" bordersize="0px" bordercolor="#e5e4e4" paddingTop="0px" paddingBottom="0px"]\r\n\r\n[one_half]\r\n[imageframe lightbox="No" style="none" bordercolor="" bordersize="0px" stylecolor="" align="right"]\r\n<img src="http://grocerye.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/sf-map.png" alt="" />[/imageframe]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n\r\n[one_half last="yes"]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center; font-size: 31px !important; color: #F68028 !important;">COVERAGE AREA, WE ARE JUST GETTING STARTED!</h1>\r\n[separator top="20" style="shadow"]\r\n<p style="color: #666; font-size: 25px !important; line-height: 30px;">We bring you back the time so you can focus on things that matter!</p>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n\r\n[/fullwidth]', 'h